casebody.data:
Tina WALDEIER and Paul Waldeier, Plaintiffs-Petitioners,
v.
PIPER 1 TOWNHOUSE CONDOMINIUM ASSOCIATION, Defendant-Respondent,
and
City of Ocean City, Defendant. C-655 September Term 2017
080434 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 9, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000257-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
